<h1>闲</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#cc7700;">xián</span><span class=alesi>(xian2)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 闲 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 闲</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/fence" style="color:black;">fence</a>, <a href="/dictionary/guard" style="color:black;">guard</a>; <a href="/dictionary/defend" style="color:black;">defend</a>; idle time</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 7<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 7 strokes: <a href="/character/我" title="wo3: our, us, i, me, my, we">我</a>, <a href="/character/这" title="zhe4: this, the, here">这</a>, <a href="/character/来" title="lai2: come, coming; return, returning">来</a>, <a href="/character/时" title="shi2: time, season; era, age, period">时</a>, <a href="/character/你" title="ni3: you, second person pronoun">你</a>, <a href="/character/作" title="zuo4: make; work; compose, write; act, perform">作</a>, <a href="/character/里" title="li3: unit of distance; village; lane">里</a>, <a href="/character/没" title="mei2: not, have not, none; drown, sink">没</a>, <a href="/character/还" title="hai2: still, yet, also, besides">还</a>, <a href="/character/进" title="jin4: advance, make progress, enter">进</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/門" title="Kangxi radical 169">門</a>&nbsp;169.4</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 5 <br><small>Other HSK 5 characters: <a href="/character/飘" title="piao1: whirlwind, cyclone; floating">飘</a>, <a href="/character/册" title="ce4: book, volume, register, list">册</a>, <a href="/character/惠" title="hui4: favor, benefit, confer kindness">惠</a>, <a href="/character/欣" title="xin1: happy, joyous, delighted">欣</a>, <a href="/character/频" title="pin2: frequently, again and again">频</a>, <a href="/character/届" title="jie4: numerary adjunct for time, term">届</a>, <a href="/character/递" title="di4: hand over, deliver; substitute">递</a>, <a href="/character/驶" title="shi3: sail, drive, pilot; fast, quick">驶</a>, <a href="/character/撞" title="zhuang4: knock against, bump into, collide">撞</a>, <a href="/character/肃" title="su4: pay respects; reverently">肃</a> <a href="/character-list/hsk/level-5" title="List of HSK 5 